// jdbc -Java database connectivity
7 step to connect the java database with java front end
1. import the package--- java.sql.*;
2.(a) load the driver----( for different different databases we have different different drivers)
  (b) register the driver
3. establish a connection
4.create the statement (1. normal 2. prepared 3. callable{this is for prepared statements})
5.execute the query
6.Exit